OL,3,CShamima Begum: Court rules against
OL,4,Crunaway IS member's citizenship appeal
OL,6,FITV News' Warren Nettleford explains
OL,7,Fthe background around Shamima Begum's
OL,8,Flong-running legal battles
OL,10,Fhas lost a Court of Appeal challenge
OL,11,Fover the removal of her British
OL,12,Fcitizenship.
OL,14,FMs Begum travelled to in 2015, at 15-
OL,15,Fyears-old, before her citizenship was
OL,16,Frevoked on national security grounds
OL,17,Fshortly after she was found in a
OL,18,FSyrian refugee camp in February 2019.
