OL,3,CShamima Begum: Court rules against
OL,4,Crunaway IS member's citizenship appeal
OL,6,FLast year, the now 24-year-old lost a
OL,7,Fchallenge against the decision at the
OL,8,FSpecial Immigration Appeals Commission
OL,9,F(SIAC).
OL,11,FMs Begum's lawyers brought a bid to
OL,12,Foverturn that decision at the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal, with the Home Office opposing
OL,14,Fthe challenge.
OL,16,FIn a ruling on Friday, three judges
OL,17,Fdismissed Ms Begum's bid.
