OL,6,FIn response to the decision, her
OL,7,Fsolicitor has promised her and the
OL,8,Fgovernment "we are not going to stop
OL,9,Ffighting until she does get justice
OL,10,Fand until she is safely back home".
OL,12,FSpeaking outside the Royal Courts of
OL,13,FJustice, Gareth Peirce said: "Shamima
OL,14,FBegum is held unlawfully in indefinite
OL,15,Farbitrary detention, which is banned
OL,16,Fby every international treaty.
