OL,6,F"She and others, other women and
OL,7,Fchildren, are in what is not a refugee
OL,8,Fcamp but a prison camp, and that is
OL,9,Fconceded by the United Kingdom, which
OL,10,Fhas stated to the UN that it agrees
OL,11,Fthat Geneva Convention articles apply.
OL,13,F"Unlawful as that is, there is no
OL,14,Fexit. There is no way that she can
OL,15,Fescape from unlawful imprisonment."
OL,17,FMs Peirce later said conditions in the
OL,18,Fal-Roj camp where Ms Begum remains had
OL,19,Fworsened.
