OL,6,FGiving the ruling, Lady Chief Justice
OL,7,FBaroness Carr said: "It could be
OL,8,Fargued the decision in Ms Begum's case
OL,9,Fwas harsh. It could also be argued
OL,10,Fthat Ms Begum is the author of her own
OL,11,Fmisfortune.
OL,13,F"But it is not for this court to agree
OL,14,For disagree with either point of view."
