OL,6,FAt the appeal hearing in October,
OL,7,FSamantha Knights KC told the court the
OL,8,FGovernment had failed to consider the
OL,9,Flegal duties owed to Ms Begum as a
OL,10,Fpotential victim of trafficking or as
OL,11,Fa result of "state failures" in her
OL,12,Fcase.
