OL,3,CShamima Begum: Court rules against
OL,4,Crunaway IS member's citizenship appeal
OL,6,FHowever, in the 42-page public
OL,7,Fjudgment, Baroness Carr said: "We are
OL,8,Fnot persuaded that there was any
OL,9,Fobligation on the Secretary of State
OL,10,Fto take into account the possibility
OL,11,Fthat there might be a duty to
OL,12,Finvestigate the circumstances of Ms
OL,13,FBegum's trafficking, alternatively, to
OL,14,Fconsider whether any such
OL,15,Finvestigation as might be required
OL,16,Fwould be enhanced by her presence in
OL,17,Fthis country."
